Note: No changes were made.
ğŸ§ª Bonus: Combine with Tags
You can combine dry-run with tag filters like this:

bash
Copy
Edit
ansible-playbook playbook.yml -e "report_only=true" --tags precheck,expiry-check,report
This will:

Run prechecks

Run expiry analysis

Email you the report

But still make zero changes to your environments.

ğŸ’¡ Summary: Why This Matters
Dry-run support is:

ğŸ§ª Safe â€” No changes made, just validation

ğŸ“ˆ Auditable â€” Review what would change before doing it

ğŸ“… Schedulable â€” Run weekly/monthly for cert monitoring

ğŸ”„ Reversible â€” Flip back to report_only: false to apply changes

